nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 156 is the 134th issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the sixty-fourth published by Titan Magazines. It was released on March 10, 2015.

Star Wars Rebels Season One episode guide! Secrets revealed! Season Two latest! Sinister Agents of the Empire: Jason Isaacs and David Oyelowo Interviewed! Celebration update! What to expect at the greatest show in the galaxy!
